meta.topic: Suicide rates (top 5 states) and household gun ownership
meta.notes: Suicide rates are 2023 crude rates per 100,000 (CDC WONDER via SAVE). Gun ownership is RAND's estimated average % of adults in gun-owning households (2007–2016).
sources: CDC WONDER via SAVE (2023 state suicide rates)
RAND Gun Policy in America: State-Level Estimates of Household Firearm Ownership (avg 2007–2016)
